# This file shows the required changes to arch/arm64/Kconfig.platforms
# in the mainline Linux kernel to enable sun60i-a733 support.
#
# The ARCH_SUNXI entry already exists and covers all sunxi SoCs.
# No changes are needed to Kconfig.platforms for the SoC itself.
#
# However, you must ensure the following are enabled in your kernel config:
#
# CONFIG_ARCH_SUNXI=y
# CONFIG_ARCH_ALLWINNER=y (if it exists in your kernel version)
#
# Device-specific options will be added as drivers are implemented.
